<dl id="mwAfc"><dt id="mwAfg">On Persian culture</dt></dl>
<div class="div-col columns column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 20em; -webkit-column-width: 20em; column-width: 20em;   " about="#mwt376" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Div col","href":"./Template:Div_col"},"params":{"colwidth":{"wt":"20em"}},"i":0}},"\n* [[Iranian philosophy]]\n* [[List of Persian poets and authors]]\n* [[Persian literature]]\n* [[Persian mysticism]]\n* [[Tajik people]]\n",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"div col end","href":"./Template:Div_col_end"},"params":{},"i":1}}]}' id="mwAfk">
